In short, Candidate 1 best matches my preference for polished, harmony‑rich, thoughtfully produced and sequenced albums that reward repeated, start‑to‑finish listening; Candidate 2, while strong in its own right, leans toward the harder, hook/riff‑centered sound I stated I prefer to avoid.

