Conclusion: The double‑disc anthology aligns far more closely with my stated preference set (rhythm‑forward mixes, layered vocal arranging, cinematic production, dynamic preserving mastering, and curated sequencing), whereas the multi‑artist singles compilation, despite good mastering, conflicts with my aversion to patched‑together compilations and the need for cohesive, detail‑rich full‑disc experiences.

