Why Remastered Made In England is the better fit:
- Lead presentation and transient clarity: Made In England is described as having close‑miked, tactile piano with restored transient snap and an intimate lead vocal presented front‑and‑center. That directly matches my strong preference for bright, close‑mic lead vocals that sit immediate in the center and for preserved transient attack.
